text: Couderay is a village in Sawyer County in Wisconsin in the United States. It is on the Couderay River. In the census of 2020, there were 81 people, 35 households, and 23 families living in the village. ==References== ==Other websites== * www.couderaywisconsin.com Category:Villages in Wisconsin Category:Sawyer County, Wisconsin
title: Couderay, Wisconsin
